00:05:51.980 --> 00:05:55.900
So if you don't know how revumenib works, so essentially,

95
00:05:56.500 --> 00:05:59.680
as I mentioned, it's a protein-protein interaction inhibitor that binds to

96
00:05:59.720 --> 00:06:03.466
meninAs you can see in the cartoon on the left, so menin is a

97
00:06:04.696 --> 00:06:08.596
